snippet.title: Evercade IREM Arcade 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
IREM is coming to Evercade.

Six great titles from two decades of arcade history.
Featuring early hitters Moon Patrol and 10-Yard Fight, stone cold classics with Battle Chopper and R-Type, and arcade gems with Lightning Swords and In The Hunt.

This collection will be available in Winter 2022, and available with the Evercade EXP package.

You can pre-order in September 2022, or get it as part of the Evercade EXP Limited Edition package available at Funstock.co.uk. You can pre-order that from June 1st 2022.
